    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486920/extras/12d58d16eba097606f982b18163ce2d7.poster.avif?t=1765810866\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486920/extras/12d58d16eba097606f982b18163ce2d7.webm?t=1765810866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486920/extras/12d58d16eba097606f982b18163ce2d7.mp4?t=1765810866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >核战的硝烟尚未散去，世界已陷入更深的混乱。神秘的“风暴藤蔓”（Tempest Vines）在核战辐射的灰烬中蔓延，它既是毁灭的象征，也孕育着巨大的能量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全球防卫部队（GDF）与风暴王朝（Tempest Dynasty）两大阵营为争夺这种神秘资源展开殊死较量，而在战场阴影中，第三股势力正悄然崛起……</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由3D Realms与Slipgate Ironworks共同打造，《风暴崛起》继承了RTS黄金时代的经典玩法，融合现代游戏技术，带来快速、流畅、硬派的战斗体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486920/extras/37d2adb564f10cac33ef12ba74af1c10.poster.avif?t=1765810866\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486920/extras/37d2adb564f10cac33ef12ba74af1c10.webm?t=1765810866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486920/extras/37d2adb564f10cac33ef12ba74af1c10.mp4?t=1765810866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>重溫經典即時戰略的基地建造，體驗快速流暢且強烈的戰鬥</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>操控兩大陣營的獨特兵種，選擇GDF（全球防衛部隊）或風暴王朝（Tempest Dynasty），（第三勢力「維提族（Veti）」將於未來開放遊玩）</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>體驗兩段史詩級單人戰役，任務簡報皆有全語音演出</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独自或和朋友一起发动战争。游戏包含 3 种模式：可以在自定义游戏大厅对抗 AI，在多人匹配中进行 1v1 和 2v2 对战，或者独自挑战冲突战模式。每队最多可以容纳 500 个单位和两款独特的超级武器，发挥各阵营的独特玩法。</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在排名配對中擊敗對手、爭奪排行榜頂端，並運用Glicko-2積分系統展現實力</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>风暴已至，你将如何书写战争史诗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >立刻加入《风暴崛起》，打造传奇战局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486920/extras/51673444c89e8d1585f24eb8761fdf36.poster.avif?t=1765810866\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486920/extras/51673444c89e8d1585f24eb8761fdf36.webm?t=1765810866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486920/extras/51673444c89e8d1585f24eb8761fdf36.mp4?t=1765810866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
